663
00:26:48.695 --> 00:26:50.295
A los demás consumidores

664
00:26:50.250 --> 00:26:52.730
y aun al mismo tabernero los miraba con

665
00:26:52.730 --> 00:26:54.810
aire impertinente y altanero.

666
00:26:55.450 --> 00:26:56.650
Eran, evidentemente,

667
00:26:56.890 --> 00:26:59.050
