721
00:29:09.959 --> 00:29:11.960
Pertenezco al tzin.

722
00:29:12.839 --> 00:29:15.240
Permítame usted que me presente.

723
00:29:16.200 --> 00:29:17.560
Simon Ivanovich

724
00:29:17.560 --> 00:29:18.519
Marmeladov,

725
00:29:19.175 --> 00:29:20.535
