7721
05:00:21.931 --> 05:00:23.211
¿Quién es usted?

7722
05:00:23.851 --> 05:00:26.171
Interrogó bruscamente Razumiquín.

7723
05:00:26.571 --> 05:00:28.091
Yo me llamo Razumiquín,

7724
05:00:28.366 --> 05:00:31.086
